reviews.review_text: Good Show, Better Quality This is one of my favorite shows. The mp3 files on this upload is better than the other one on here with mp3's. It has less crowd noise and more depth. I love the brokedown on his show for some reason, even though brent messes up the lyrics a little at the end of it. I'd recommend this show.
